Package: bidsexportr
Type: Package
Title: Helps by exporting BIDS structured neuroimaging data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Niklas Wulms
Maintainer: Niklas Wulms <wulms@uni-muenster.de>
Description: Contains one function "XXXXX" that starts a user-friendly process to copy BIDS data to another destination.
    The user can select sessions, sequences and subjects for data export, which is rather sophisticated in the nested BIDS structure.
